# Census API key configuration.
#
# 1. Get a free key:  https://api.census.gov/data/key_signup.html
# 2. COPY this file to a new file named ".env"  (copy, don't rename --
#    keep this .example template in place). The real .env is git-ignored.
# 3. Paste your key after the = sign below. No quotes needed.

CENSUS_API_KEY=your_key_here
